pan></span></span></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.3117em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal mtight\" style=\"margin-right:0.05724em;\">j</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.2861em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span> 为 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span></span>，否则为 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span>。</li>\n</ul>\n<p>我们界定<strong>模块度</strong>大于 0.3-0.7 中的一个阈值的社区为 <strong>有效社区结构(significant community structure)</strong>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"anchor-a345e79478007233\" style=\"position: relative;\">2. 社区发现<a href=\"#anchor-a345e79478007233\" aria-label=\"anchor a345e79478007233 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-4febf7f816ab80b5\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.1. Louvain<a href=\"#anchor-4febf7f816ab80b5\" aria-label=\"anchor 4febf7f816ab80b5 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<p><strong>模块度增益(modularity gain)</strong> 的计算方法：<span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>Q</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>D</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>C</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>Q</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>D</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>i</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">Δ</mi><mi>Q</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>→</mo><mi>C</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\Delta Q(D\\to i\\to C)=\\Delta Q(D\\to i) + \\Delta Q(i\\to C)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6595em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">Δ</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">Q</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">i</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span>。</p>\n<p>Louvain 算法的过程如下：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><em>Phase 1</em>: (Modularity is optimized by allowing only local changes to node-communities memberships)\n<ul>\n<li><em>Step 1</em>. 将每个节点单独划分为一个社区</li>\n<li><em>Step 2</em>. 对于每个节点，计算将其放到另一社区的<strong>模块度增益</strong>，如果有 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mo>></mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">>0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span></span></span></span></span> 的就选择其中最大的放过去。</li>\n<li><em>Step 3</em>. 一直循环第二步直到划分不发生变化。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><em>Phase 2</em>: (The identified communities are aggregated into super-nodes to build a new network)\n<ul>\n<li>将划分到一个社区的点合并成一个 super-node，从而得到一个新的网络。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>这样一个完整的过程称为一个 PASS，有必要的话可以执行多个 PASS。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/09/01/P2cHnTeO.png\"alt=\"P2cHnTeO.png\" style=\"width: 547px; \" ></p>\n<h3 id=\"anchor-4235d9f68450a78a\" style=\"position: relative;\">2.2. BigCLAM<a href=\"#anchor-4235d9f68450a78a\" aria-label=\"anchor 4235d9f68450a78a permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>BigCLAM 算法可以解决社区之间有重叠的情况。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://static.memset0.cn/img/v6/2024/09/01/9f1zpP7F.png\"alt=\"9f1zpP7F.png\" style=\"width: 399px; \" ></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>TBD</p>\n<h2 id=\"anchor-b55e4a85f99e3192\" style=\"position: relative;\">3. 参考资料<a href=\"#anchor-b55e4a85f99e3192\" aria-label=\"anchor b55e4a85f99e3192 permalink\" class=\"anchor after\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://snap.stanford.edu/class/cs224w-2020/slides/13-communities.pdf\">13-communities.pdf (stanford.edu)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://huanghelouzi.blog.csdn.net/article/details/119762427\">CS224W 图机器学习笔记 13-Community Detection_network comunities-CSDN 博客</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/PolarisRisingWar/article/details/119277189\">cs224w（图机器学习）2021 冬季课程学习笔记 16 Community Detection in Networks_community detection and classification in social n-CSDN 博客</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_16543881/article/details/122825957\">社区发现算法——Louvain 算法_louvain 算法-CSDN 博客</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://seunghan96.github.io/gnn/gnn13/\">(CS224W) 13.Community Detection in Networks - AAA (All About AI) (seunghan96.github.io)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.zepengzhang.com/2021/07/26/20210726cs224w1213/\">CS224W Lecture 12 &#x26; 13 Subgraph Mining and Community Detection | Zepeng Zhang's Blog</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_16543881/article/details/123116919\">社区发现算法——BigCLAM 算法-CSDN 博客</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-2293f2a3c25c0518\">1. 基本概念</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-050897975eb0033a\">1.1. 社区</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-9088979af086cd34\">1.2. 模块度</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-a345e79478007233\">2. 社区发现</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-4febf7f816ab80b5\">2.1. Louvain</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#anchor-4235d9f68450a78a\">2.2. BigCLAM</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#anchor-b55e4a85f99e3192\">3. 参考资料</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"社区发现","date":null,"description":null},"fields":{"cover":null,"slug":"/course/cs224w/note/community-detection/","isDoc":true,"category":"[{\"name\":\"课程笔记\",\"to\":\"/course/\"}]","propsJson":null}},"previous":null,"next":null},"pageContext":{"id":"e73b6703-f2a1-5926-8857-c8fd5d5fcf6c","previousPostId":null,"nextPostId":null,"navJson":"[{\"slug\":\"/course/cs224w\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/cs224w/index.md\",\"title\":\"Intro\"},{\"title\":\"Notes\",\"children\":[{\"slug\":\"/course/cs224w/note/graph-neural-networks\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/cs224w/note/graph-neural-networks.md\",\"title\":\"图神经网络\"},{\"slug\":\"/course/cs224w/note/graph-augmentation\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/cs224w/note/graph-augmentation.md\",\"title\":\"图增强\"},{\"slug\":\"/course/cs224w/note/knowledge-graph\",\"file\":\"/home/runner/work/gatsby-blog/gatsby-blog/content/course/cs224w/note/knowledge-graph.md\",\"title\":\"知识图谱\"},{\"slug\":\"/c